reviewText: While the movie is not A-level, the Cajun environment is interesting/different (the swamp setting, language, music), the story entertaining (though not always pleasant); but the most special aspect of this movie for me is beautiful actress Jan MacKenzie!
summary: I would buy this "cult movie" if available on DVD!
